{
  "design_notes": "The chart is built for Medium players with a focus on steady flows, clear accenting on drop downbeats, and utilizing vocal hold sections. Intro (Bar 0-16) maps basic beats with simple 8th-note syncopations to match the buildup. Drop 1 (Bar 16-24) introduces sustained vocal holds layered over a steady drive. S2 build (Bar 24-36) returns to running-man-styled movements on vocal cuts. S3 drop (Bar 36-52) increases step density into full 8th-note streams punctuated by brief, comfortable hold sections. S4 bridge (Bar 52-64) lightens step counts before S5 quiet outro (Bar 64-74) eases the player into a smooth stop.",
